								      <td align="left" colspan=2><span class="newsbody">We are going to be redesigning the website.  I may start from scratch and design it from the ground up again.  If you have any of the following skills...<BR><BR><img src="images/bullets.gif">HTML<BR><img src="images/bullets.gif">Cascading Style Scripts(CSS)<BR><img src="images/bullets.gif">Javascript<BR><img src="images/bullets.gif">Active Server Pages(ASP)<BR><img src="images/bullets.gif">Graphics Design<BR><img src="images/bullets.gif">Webdesign & Layout<BR><BR>And you want to help, please send me an email and let me know how you wish to help.  I will begin work on the new site soon.  I most likely will not be online very much if I am solely taking on the redesign again, just so you know.  The last redesign took some time to complete and I feel that this one will as well.  I am going to cut a few options from the new site and maybe add them in later if the options are that useful.<BR>My main goal is to provide the guild with a place to link to our forum, provide a guild roster, and keep the guild up to date on the raids and events we are holding.  I"ll keep you up to date as the progress and when it begins.<BR><BR>Aliseisu Dryaden<BR><font size=1><i>CotGD Webmaster/Guild Leader</i></font></span><br><br></td>
